### Get all unique MAC addresses
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sysinfo/devices

### Get metadata for a specific MAC address
# @name get_devices_by_mac
# @ref Get all unique MAC addresses
# @prompt MAC_ADDR Please replace with a valid MAC address from the previous response.
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sysinfo/devices?mac_addr={{MAC_ADDR}}

### (Expected to fail) Get metadata for a non-existent MAC address
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sysinfo/devices?mac_addr=00:00:00:00:00:00
